idence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31883,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/abu-huraira-speech-deeds-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":6031,"position":3},"title":"Abu Huraira on Akhlaq: Speech part of deeds, character part of religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dahhak reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever does not view his speech as part of his deeds and his character as part of his religion, he will be ruined without realizing it.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323amt wa \u0100da\u0304b al-Lisa\u0304n 560 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0636\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0643\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/21\/dahhak-al-sayyid-hasan-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":6031,"position":4},"title":"Dahhak on Character: Head of the matter is good character","aut